FORM CORR_MAINT_ZABSF_PP_V_EQUI USING VALUE(CM_ACTION) RC.
  DATA: RETCODE LIKE SY-SUBRC, COUNT TYPE I, TRSP_KEYLEN TYPE SYFLENG.
  FIELD-SYMBOLS: <TAB_KEY_X> TYPE X.
  CLEAR RC.
MOVE ZABSF_PP_V_EQUI-ID TO
ZABSF_EQUIPMENTS-ID .
MOVE ZABSF_PP_V_EQUI-AREAID TO
ZABSF_EQUIPMENTS-AREAID .
